  "detailed_description": "<br><br><strong>Tanks, But No Tanks</strong> is an updated take on a classic top-down arena tank shooter. This <strong>multiplayer madhouse</strong> will keep you on your toes as you balance <strong>collecting coins</strong> on each map with <strong>shooting projectiles</strong> at your foes. <strong>Upgrade</strong> your tank’s weapons, armor, and special abilities in between rounds with the coins you accrue.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631630/extras/091eaa8588dc7445628276f162956f13.poster.avif?t=1695647522\" width=590 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631630/extras/091eaa8588dc7445628276f162956f13.webm?t=1695647522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Use your mouse or a controller to aim your bullets and shoot your way through each level. Just be sure that you don't ricochet a bullet right back toward yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631630/extras/39e1ed160a690cc07793cef32359024c.poster.avif?t=1695647522\" width=590 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631630/extras/39e1ed160a690cc07793cef32359024c.webm?t=1695647522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Use a diverse weapon set, ranging from <strong>deployable turrets</strong> to <strong>teleportation projectiles </strong>to cause extra mayhem on the battlefield!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631630/extras/20a04a0baf814dd704e412a007f5eeee.poster.avif?t=1695647522\" width=590 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631630/extras/20a04a0baf814dd704e412a007f5eeee.webm?t=1695647522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>15+ Unique Levels (With More In Development!)<br>    </li><li>15+ Weapon & Character Upgrades<br>    </li><li>Tournament Style Play Rewards The Player Who Survives The Most Rounds<br>    </li><li>Full Controller Support<br>    </li><li>Play With Up To 4 Local Players<br>    </li><li>Different Game Modes Including Free-For-All & Teams<br>    </li><li>Adjustable Bot Difficulty</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631630/extras/22afa2ae451fe7d35cd21c1512094ec9.poster.avif?t=1695647522\" width=590 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631630/extras/22afa2ae451fe7d35cd21c1512094ec9.webm?t=1695647522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
